ca.ualberta.moodroid.ui

Class MoodListAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<MoodListAdapter.ViewHolder>
      • ca.ualberta.moodroid.ui.MoodListAdapter

  • public class MoodListAdapter
extends androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<MoodListAdapter.ViewHolder>
    This is a custom adapter meant for displaying moods according to the assignment spec. It takes the mood data the user creates and displays it with its colour, emoji, and title.
